ahead to Robitaille.

942
01:24:21,440 --> 01:24:24,040
Not much time to go. Luc Robitaille...

943
01:24:30,280 --> 01:24:33,720
We've got eight seconds left!

944
01:24:38,080 --> 01:24:40,000
Seconds to go.

945
01:24:57,600 --> 01:24:59,480
Stop the press!
Stop the press!

946
01:24:59,520 --> 01:25:01,400
