972
01:29:29,520 --> 01:29:32,840
Bang! I'm immortal.

973
01:30:20,280 --> 01:30:22,000
Aah!

974
01:31:25,000 --> 01:31:28,120
Aaaah!

975
01:31:47,200 --> 01:31:49,760
Jagr will carry it in,
